Acme/please version 0.01
========================

exports a variable $please to the callers space, which will
randomly evaluate to the empty string three quarters of the time
and to "please" the rest.

tie options exist to tweak the fraction of time it says please,
and also what language it says please in.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


